video_title: Why holding onto what you can't control is "a fool's game." #wisdom #jayshetty
transcript:
most of us are conditioned to believe
when you find something good hold on to
it forever make sure it lasts forever
because you never know and I love your
perspective because I think not only is
it healthier for the mind and the ego
it's actually the reality of life that
everything is ephemeral and transient
and it will move anyway yeah and so you
wanting to hold on to something that
isn't yours to control is almost a
Fool's game anyway
